status.name: status
status.description: The overall status of the RackCDU. Status is evaluated based on the notification settings. If a noticiation has been disabled it will not be included in the overall status either.

notifyTable.name: notifyTable
notifyTable.description: Table of settings used to setup notifications.

notifyEntry.name: notifyEntry
notifyEntry.description: Single notify entry containing notification receiver info.

notifyEnabled.name: notifyEnabled
notifyEnabled.description: Indicates if this notify entry is enabled or not.

notifyCommunity.name: notifyCommunity
notifyCommunity.description: Notification community to be used by agent to send trap.

temperatureFacilityIn.name: temperatureFacilityIn
temperatureFacilityIn.description: The temperature of the water going into the RackCDU on the Facility side (cold).

temperatureFacilityOut.name: temperatureFacilityOut
temperatureFacilityOut.description: The temperature of the water going out of the RackCDU on the Facility side (hot).

temperatureServerIn.name: temperatureServerIn
temperatureServerIn.description: The temperature of the water going into the servers node (cold).

temperatureServerOut.name: temperatureServerOut
temperatureServerOut.description: The temperature of the water going out of the servers node (hot).

temperatureAmbient.name: temperatureAmbient
temperatureAmbient.description: The temperature of the ambient air close to the RackCDU.

pressureServer.name: pressureServer
pressureServer.description: The pressure inside the RackCDU on the server side.

pressureFacility.name: pressureFacility
pressureFacility.description: The pressure inside the RackCDU on the facility side.

serverLeak.name: serverLeak
serverLeak.description: Boolean indication of whether the RackCDU has detected a leak in the system.

serverLevel.name: serverLevel
serverLevel.description: Boolean indication of whether the RackCDU has detected a low level of cooleant.

flowFacility.name: flowFacility
flowFacility.description: The flow of the cooleant on the facility side.

heatload.name: heatload
heatload.description: The heatload of the cooleant on the facility side. Can be averaged from e.g. 1 to 28800 (24 hours) sec.

modeOfOperation.name: modeOfOperation
modeOfOperation.description: Mode of operation of ControlBox, can be agent or master.

ipSrc.name: ipSrc
ipSrc.description: IP address source of ControlBox, eg. static or dhcp.

controllerOutAlpha.name: controllerOutAlpha
controllerOutAlpha.description: Controller Out Alpha - damping factor of output.

fluidHeatCapacity.name: fluidHeatCapacity
fluidHeatCapacity.description: Heat Capacity of the liquid coolant utilized in the facility loop.

heatAverageFactor.name: heatAverageFactor
heatAverageFactor.description: The time frame of which the heat load is averaged. A short time frame make the heat load sensative to small changes is temperature and flow which results in a highly fluctuating value. A long time frame stabilizes the value, but also results in a long response time.

harnessVersion.name: harnessVersion
harnessVersion.description: Must be set to the harness version utilized by the RackCDU. The harness version may affect the functionality of the RackCDU and it it therefor important that the versions is matched.
